Package: sciehr
Type: Package
Title: Bridge ICU Electronic Health Records for Spinal Cord Injury Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marzieh", "Mussavi Rizi",
           email   = "mmussavirizi@uwaterloo.ca",
           role    = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "")),
    person("Vlad", "",
           role = "aut")
  )
Description: A full-stack pipeline for extracting, harmonizing, and loading
    electronic health record (EHR) data from MIMIC-III, MIMIC-IV, and eICU
    into PostgreSQL. sci_ehr automates cohort construction, concept
    extraction, unit conversion, and assembly of analysis-ready time-series
    and flat outcome tables — purpose-built for spinal cord injury (SCI)
    critical care research.
